<author>mạhr fạyz, mạhr fạyz</author>
<title>klạmk ạ̉nt rwḥ wḥyạẗ</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- ( klạmk ạ̹nt rwḥ wḥyạẗ wnwrk ạ̹nt bhạʾ ạllh )2
 ạlqrạr - yswʿ .. ( dh mstny lqạk ạ̹mty̱ hạkwn wyạk )2
 ( ạ̹nt slạmy wnwr ạ̉yạmy )2 yạ yswʿy
 2- ( wmwtk ạ̹nt dh kạn ly ḥyạẗ wṣlbk ạ̹nt dh kạn ly njạẗ ) 2
 3- ( wḥḍnk ạ̹nt dh klh ḥnạn wḥbk ạ̹nt dh br ạ̉mạn )2
 4- ( ftḥt qlby skn jwạh wrḥk ạ̹nt mạlyny ḥyạẗ )2
 5- ( ạ̹lhy rby ạ̹jʿlny ṣlạẗ yṣly qlby wạqwl wyạh )2</lyrics>
</song>